<p>And you could always find a reason to postpone why you should buy that share of Coca-Cola. But the important thing wasnâ€™t to see that. The important thing was to see they were going to be selling a billion eight-ounce servings of beverages a day this year. Or some large number. And that the person who could make people happy a billion times a day around the globe ought to make a few bucks off doing it.</p>

